message.entry: Index must be a finite 3-digit number of the format mnp.
Requires valid axes handle for input.
Index must be a 3-digit number of the format mnp.
Position must be of the form [left bottom width height].
Function called with too many output arguments.
Calling subplot with a handle to a {0} is not supported.
Setting {0} is not supported with subplot. This syntax will no longer be supported in a future release.
subplot ignores grid location arguments when Position is specified. This syntax will no longer be supported in a future release.
Adding subplots to a container with the ''AutoResizeChildren'' property set to ''on'' is not supported.
